column5: out on the grand this morning seems like there is 3 to 4 inches of good ice.
I wanna go on sat,but with the forecast calling for rain, the river may swell esp at the bottom end.It may be an iffy for me.

I was out for a few hours on Tuesday afternoon. Unfortunately no fish for me.  There were about 15 guys out there altogether.  If you are going, stop in at Fishmasters, Steve will tell you which areas to stay clear of.  There were still a couple of open spots on Tuesday.  Cheers  Craig
